{
  "key_path": "ChangeGuestsTypeToManager",
  "content": "Guest <strong>{{userName}}</strong> will be moved to the {{membersSection}} section and assigned the <strong>'{{ secondType }}'</strong> type. Room admins can create and manage the assigned rooms, invite new users, and assign roles of Room admin and lower. Room admins have access to the {{documentsSection}} section.",
  "content_en_sha1_hash": "8fa73538c8eb1bc56fc6fe99b61cc6805ef55867",
  "created_at": "2025-05-19T21:30:56.922Z",
  "updated_at": "2026-04-11T21:04:02.205Z",
  "comment": {
    "text": "This is a confirmation message in a dialog that appears when changing a guest's role to \"Room Admin\". It informs the user about the new role's permissions and where the user will be moved. `{{userName}}` is the guest's name, `{{membersSection}}` is the name of the section where the user will be moved, `{{secondType}}` is the new role name (\"Room Admin\"), and `{{documentsSection}}` is the name of the section they will have access to.",
    "is_auto": true,
    "updated_at": "2026-04-11T21:04:02.205Z",
    "model": "google/gemini-2.5-flash"
  },
  "usage": [
    {
